name: Ess
adError:
Ú-cennen ad.
I app guren lín guren.
adErrorFix: Echuia aníron lin o i 'lû o govad i-dagor lín.
blockedProInfo: Aníra Pro-vad an ú-barthad a ú-lû.
importInformation:
An rochad i nadhad, i nadhad lín aníron hain na-chened.
Dan rochad, hain nadhad lín achened ú-gar.

Gerich naid a lín?
helpExport: Natho aníron echad i nadhad lín na ennorath adlant?
helpExportAns:
Nae, hain aníron ned i estel. Na i estel lín, estel dîn echad i nadhad a danno i ennorath adlant.
Na i ennorath adlant, natho aníron rochad hain nadhad.
helpExportSecurity: Gerich i nadhad lín cenid ned echad?
helpExportSecurityAns: Nae, i nadhad lín lîn cenid e-chad o chened hain ú-chennar. Mal no er, in-rach i chened adar hain chennar.
helpAddAns:
Aníron nadhad bain lín ned dau ein:
Naethad an '"+"' ned i pan i nadhad lín na i gwest.
O naethad an '"+"' na i ven i dair lín.
helpEditAns: Aníron nadhad lín athrad ned i dair i gwest lín. Le thand an i pen 'stang' na i nadhad lín.
helpRemoveAns: Le thand lad nadhad naethad i danad nad na 0.
helpAddCatAns:
Le thand desta nadhad gwest ned i estel 'Adda Rathad'.

Ae dant i thand lín ú-bad, na 4 nadhad gwest aníron.
helpEditCatAns: Nadhad gwest aníron athrad naethad i pen 'stang' ned i estel lín.
helpRemCatAns:
Nadhad gwest aníron lad naethad i cened nad na 0.

Bain nadhad i gwest aníron thand na "{unassigned}".
helpRemCatExpense: Gerich i nadhad lín lad naethad nadhad gwest?
helpRemCatExpenseAns: Ú-bad, bain nadhad lín thand thand na "{unassigned}".
helpAutoExp: Man aníron pensad nadhad bain na 'lû-mîl'?
helpAutoExpAns: Na i tîr "{autoexpenses}" le thand pensad hain na nadhad gwest.
helpEditAutoExp: Man i berad aníron athrad nadhad bain?
helpEditAutoExpAns: Dan, bain nadhad naeg lain pen achenad. I bain nadhad lín ú-channad.
helpRemAutoExpAns:
Le thand lad naethad i cened nad na 0.
I bain nadhad lín ú-bad.
helpRemAutoExpOldExp: Gerich i bain nadhad lín lad dan athrad nadhad bain?
helpRemAutoExpOldExpAns: Ú-bad, i bain nadhad lín thand.
helpOldRangesAns:
Le thand pen na i gwest naer "{currentRange}". Na dan, pen i thîr 'lû-mîl gîn'.

Na Pro-vad le thand cenad i 2 'lû-mîl gîn. Na Free-vad na 6 'lû-mîl gîn.
helpInternet: Aníron lû gwened na i Internet?
helpInternetAns:
Ú-er a lín app-vad.

Pro-vad ú-er na naer, Free-vad gerich a thand.
helpDataStorageAns: I nadhad lín thand an i annar lín. Ú-er i beditha i annar lín.
helpBusinessDayAns: I lû thîr hain naen na Ven a Orain. I lanth i 'lû thîr ú-gwestad.
helpCatOrder: Man aníron athrad i tîr nadhad gwest?
helpCatOrderAns: Le thand athrad nadhad gwest ned i estel. Le thand thand i pen i dîn nadhad gwest a thand i naer.
helpStatistics: Man aníron cenad i nadhad bain ned hûl?
helpStatisticsAns: Na i gwaithath naer aen. Le thand cenad i naeg a rathad nadhad bain i 'lû-mîl ennas na i 'lû naer.
helpStatToSmallAns: Le thand lethon na i daurath a chened. Na dan, i gwaithath thand a cenad hain.
helpFilter: Aníron cenad nadhad gwest naen aníron?
helpFilterAns:
Nae.
Le thand pen na i rathad naer, aníron i nadhad lain thand.
Na dan, i cened na i nadhad gwest thand.

Na i hûl naer, nerad lân thand cenad. Le thand pen i rathad naer a thand naer.
helpYAxis: Aníron cened i gwest naid be nadad?
helpYAxisAns: Ú-er naid aníron. I thelin naeg hain.
helpCryptic: Cenin hain an-cheniath, man thand cenin?
helpCrypticAns:
Ú-bad na. Dan a lín i no hain ú-gennad. Aníron thand dan o i estel a govad.
Cerin i 'nathad lín a govad i chel o i estel lín.
helpDev: Aníron cenad o i adlannath a lín app?
helpDevAns:
Ú-er i nathad dan. I app na adlant a govad na erin.
Natho nathad aestel.

Na dan, dan estel thand a i app-estel naer thand.
upgradeToUnlock: Ceved Pro-Vad aníron a theled bain naen!
purchasePending: I nathad lín na rîd. Avo pêd a si
purchaseFailed: I nathad ú-rîd. Avo pêd a si dan.
benefits: I mae hain na mîn na vedui:
benefitList:
- Ú-adlant adnann
- Adlant nadhad gwest
- Adlant pensad bathad
- Aníron cenad a govad na {maxPro} (na {maxFree}) 'lû-mîl
helpPrivacy: Man aníron cenad i thand i mellonath?
helpPrivacyAns: Le thand cenad i mellonath an i thel lín (Engl.):
helpMoveExpAns:
Nae, tîr lín aníron na i arodadath adel i nauthad.
Edregol lín dîn vi i goll lín edregol.
helpMoveAutoAns: Nae, tîr lín aníron na i arodadath adel edregol bain vi i goll.
helpMoveAutoOld: Gerich i bathad lín hen nadad edregol naid?
helpMoveAutoOldAns: Ú-naid, i bathad lín hen ú-thand.
helpAutoModes: Man aníron thand i bathad bain lín?
helpAutoModesAns: Cenatha lín bain i aurad, i achadad, i ardhad a i rindad.
helpAutoChange: Man naid gerich nadad lûr i bathad bain?
helpAutoChangeAns: I nadad lín i bathad lín ú-dínad aníron naid i lûr nín. I bathad hen thand bain.
helpProUpgradeAns:
Tîr lín aníron adel vi i aran 'Pro-Vad'. Na nathad vi i nedhuin.

Mâ tîr lín ú-goll, le natho Pro-Vad.
helpShowRemaining: Mâd lín egorath i ratha adlant na chenedath?
helpShowRemainingAns: Nae, tîr lín aníron na i estelath. Aníron, ú-adlant cenatha, adlant cenatha linna.
helpRanges: Ú-thand lín nadad lûr lín na si a chebin lín.
helpRangesAns: Sa i hain thand, tîr lín aníron an i nadad bain hain thand vi bain. Bain naid lín dîn nall.
introS1Body:
Mâd lín i hain ned i ardhad, nauthad a arodadath lín gwenith a mathad.

Aníron lín aníron i ardhad bathad aníron?
introS2Body: Achenatha nadad bain aníron lín edregol?
introS3Body:
Tîr lín i naid edregol.
(Pure Budget-naid: *.pbstate)
introS4Body: Man i aearad aníron lín gwenith i ardhad?
introS5Body: Tîr lín i ardhad bain naid:
introS6Body: Tîr lín i arodadath (e.g. lû thîw, aníron gûr, lû bain):
introS7Body: Tîr lín i nauthad bain (e.g. dîr, lû lín tûr):
introS8Body:
Hannon le aníron {appName}! Gerich gûr aníron lín gwenith i ardhad.

I hain a aníron aníron lín dîn goll thand lín erin dîn edregol.
sharedDbAlreadyExists:
Dúath: Naur e-cheniad.

Aníron na i ardhon lín gwenien!
newSharedDb: Aníron: Naur narn a i ardhon lín dollen.
sDbConnectionFailedInfo: Genna heniaid naur dadh. Pedo athrad!
authText: Eitha i nadad acheniel na carch
keyInputInfo: Ped i carch lín egor cilith i carch cilith
helpSharedDbGeneralAns: Heniaid naur linna na innas pedin. Gi thand i mae lín a gellin a linnad lín edregol.
helpSharedDbInvis: Ú-cenin naur heniaid naur nedh i dannen
helpSharedDbInvisAns: Aníron aníron nadad lín na Pro edregol o {appName}.
helpSharedDbConnectAns:
Gi genna heniaid naur nedh i dannen.

Pedo nedh dannen i rath i heniaid naur. Pedo dannen lín o rath. Man ú-chad heniaid, nadad lín goll.
helpSharedDbSec: Man na vedui i mae lín?
helpSharedDbSecAns: Heniaid naur teitha narn. I carch lín eched. Nadad lín aníron na genna carch o heniaid chen.
helpSharedDbKeyAns: Cenin nedh dannen lín. Cenith cilith egor peth.
helpSharedDbDisconnect: Man nadad aníron nadad heniaid naur?
helpSharedDbDisconnectAns: I linnad lín bediath lín. Nadad lín, ach nedh heniaid nadad lín.
helpSharedDbNoConnection: Man pedin man ú-genna heniaid, an ú-thannad lín?
helpSharedDbNoConnectionAns: Goll lín nadad nedh gwaith a pedo nadad lín aníron na genna heniaid.
helpSharedDbIndicatorAns:
Gwennath aen na dîn i naur. 4 dadad:
1. Naur nen: Genna.
2. Naur darth: Genna nadad.
3. Naur nedh certh: Gwaith naer.
4. Ú-naur: Ú-genna heniaid.
helpSharedDbResync: Man genna gwaith naer nedh heniaid naur?
remote_select:
Rîw pado
(Târ an i lû adlant edregol)
rotateInfo: I carch nedhannen an i gwaith lín ú-vadad na '{updateEncryptKey}'.
helpRmDBSync: Man hain gwaith na heniaid naur gannad?
helpRmDBSyncAns: Pediad hain gwaith 2, orchal a peniad. A hain gwaith 2 an nedh tûr a dadad carch.
helpRmDBRotate: Man pedin an dadad i carch na heniaid naur lín?
helpRmDBRotateAns: Pediad hain gwaith nedh dannen heniaid naur. Pedich i carch ú-vadad an i gwaith lín.
helpRmDBRefresh: Man pedin an nedhannen carch ú-aníron dadad heniaid a nadad lín goll?
helpRmDBRefreshAns: Pediad hain gwaith 'Carch nedhannen' nedh dannen heniaid naur.
helpScannerAns: Nae, i Pro-adan na Android ar IOS, nadad rûth thand. I naid bain cheneg a thand na i gwannoed category. Ach nadad egor, nadad cened acheniad, aníron nadad
helpScannerLocAns:
Pân nadad na nathron:

- Cennad na naid hebed na i symbol camera
- Pedh na i budget pot a pedh
- Pedh na i 'Overview' na naid
- Na i symbol camera na naid na idhlithad adloth
